dct_title_s: State of New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection Division of Marine Services: Map showing lands under tide-water situate in the Township of Brick, in the County of Ocean
dct_description_sm: Map shows the grant covering Block 22 of Normandy Drive & Ellison Drive. Map features include Route 35, Ellis Tide Pond, and Barnegat Bay.
